@startuml process_view_3_4
actor Treasurer
participant "MinutesForm" as UI
participant "MeetingValidator" as Val
participant "Firebase/Firestore" as DB

Treasurer -> UI: Enter Minutes & Click Save
UI -> UI: Construct MeetingInput
UI -> Val: validateMeetingInput(input, now, isRecordingMinutes=true)
activate Val
Val -> Val: Check if isRecordingMinutes
note right: Mid-Sprint Change:\nBypass future date check
Val --> UI: { isValid: true }
deactivate Val

UI -> DB: updateDoc(meetingRef, { minutes })
activate DB
DB --> UI: Success
deactivate DB
UI -> Treasurer: Show Success Toast
@enduml